FROM --platform=$BUILDPLATFORM node:24-slim@sha256:6f7b03f7c2c8e2e784dcf9295400527b9b1270fd37b7e9a7285cf83b6951452d AS build
ENV PNPM_HOME="/pnpm"
ENV PATH="$PNPM_HOME:$PATH"
RUN corepack enable
COPY . /app
WORKDIR /app
RUN --mount=type=cache,id=pnpm,target=/pnpm/store pnpm install --frozen-lockfile
RUN pnpm run build

FROM joseluisq/static-web-server:2.43.0
COPY --from=build /app/dist /public
